					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This skip wants to be a character piece, not unlike <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cadavercommander" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3187823&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1592702846" alt="CadaverCommander" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3187823)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/cadavercommander" >CadaverCommander</a></span>'s character driven pieces, but this does not sell me on this character. Its attributes are all over the place: it's walking talking corn that's narcissistic and hates goats and people that eat corn and makes machines and it's all too much. The dialogue is hard to read as well; I cannot get a grip on the flow of the conversation or how these characters speak.</p> <p>A -1 from me.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
